## 🚀 To Get Started (3 Simple Steps)

### Step 1: Setup Database
```bash
# Create database
psql -U postgres
CREATE DATABASE prodev_db;
\q

# Run schema
psql -U postgres -d prodev_db -f Database/schema.sql
```

### Step 2: Update Configuration
Edit `appsettings.json` dan ganti:
```
"Password=YOUR_PASSWORD_HERE"
```
dengan password PostgreSQL kamu.

### Step 3: Run Application
```bash
dotnet run
```

Dialog "Koneksi database berhasil!" akan muncul ✅

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```
Form1 (Windows Forms UI)
  ↓
DeveloperService (Business Logic - Async)
  ↓
DeveloperRepository / PerformanceRepository (Data Access)
  ↓
DatabaseConnection (Npgsql)
  ↓
PostgreSQL Database (prodev_db)
```

