## 🎯 Key Technologies Used

- **C# 13.0** - Language
- **.NET 9** - Framework
- **Windows Forms** - UI Framework
- **Npgsql 10.0.0** - PostgreSQL driver
- **PostgreSQL** - Database
- **Async/Await** - Asynchronous programming
- **Repository Pattern** - Data access abstraction
- **Service Layer** - Business logic separation

---

## 📊 Database Structure

### Tables
- **developers** - Store developer information
- **performances** - Store developer performance metrics
- Foreign key relationship (performances → developers)
- Cascade delete enabled
- Indexes for optimization

### Features
- Timestamps (created_at, updated_at) untuk tracking
- Performance score calculation (quality based on bugs)
- Performance rating (Excellent, Good, Average, Needs Improvement)

